b/API/Window/vrdisplaypresentchange_event\"><code>vrdisplaypresentchange</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概要","title":"概要","isH3":false,"content":"<p>ウィンドウを文書内の特定の位置までスクロールします。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">window.scroll(x-coord,y-coord)\nwindow.scroll(options)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"引数","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><code>x-coord</code> : 左上を基準とした、表示させたい文書の水平軸上のピクセル</li>\n  <li><code>y-coord</code> : 左上を基準とした、表示させたい文書の垂直軸上のピクセル</li>\n</ul>\n<p>または</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><code>options</code> : 三つのプロパティを持たせられるオブジェクト\n    <ul>\n      <li><code>top</code> <code>y-coord</code> と同じです</li>\n      <li><code>left</code> <code>x-coord</code> と同じです``</li>\n      <li><code>behavior</code> <code>smooth</code>、 <code>instant</code>、 <code>auto</code> のうちどれか一つを含む文字列。初期値は <code>auto</code> です</li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 100 個目の垂直ピクセル上にウィンドウの最上部を配置します。 --&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">onClick</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value javascript language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">scroll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>click to scroll down 100 pixels<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"スクロールの動作を変更する\">スクロールの動作を変更する</h4>\n<p>スクロールの仕方を変えたいなら、options で指定してください</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scroll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">top</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">behavior</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"smooth\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"注記","title":"注記","isH3":false,"content":"<p>効果としては、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/scrollTo\"><code>window.scrollTo</code></a> もこのメソッドと同じです。 繰り返し特定の距離をスクロールさせるには <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/scrollBy\"><code>window.scrollBy</code></a> を使用してください。</p>\n<p>次のページもご覧下さい : <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/scrollByLines\"><code>window.scrollByLines</code></a> 、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/scrollByPages\"><code>window.scrollByPages</code></a> 、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element/scrollIntoView\"><code>Element.scrollIntoView()</code></a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Specification</th>\n      <th>Status</th>\n      <th>Comment</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/#dom-window-scroll\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM) View Module<br><small lang=\"ja\">window.scroll() の定義</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n      <td>Initial definition.</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概要","id":"概要"},{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"注記","id":"注記"},{"text":"仕様","id":"仕様"}],"summary":"ウィンドウを文書内の特定の位置までスクロールします。","popularity":0.0005,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window.scroll()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Window.scroll()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Window.scroll()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Window.scroll()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Window.scroll()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Window.scroll()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/window/scroll","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/window/scroll/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"Window"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/scroll","title":"window.scroll"}],"pageTitle":"window.scroll - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}